    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Dear Molly, </p>
<p>Everything&#39;s coming up radishes. I had braised radishes at a restaurant last week, and magically, I liked them. </p>
<p>I&#39;ve hated radishes my whole life. They taste peppery and make my mouth itch! Only once as I kid do I remember liking radishes &#8211; when my mom made them into sticks and we dunked them into some vanilla milk. </p>
<p>So&#8230;with the restaurant last week and your post, I think that fate is telling me to give radishes a second try. If you think they are worth it, they must be worth a braise. </p>
<p>Thanks for writing, and thank you for posting at 10:30 at night. Makes me feel better for posting at crazy hours on my blog. </p>
<p>Best, </p>
<p>Kate</p>
