  <li id="comment-24321" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="http://thewellwornapron.blogspot.com/" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Angela</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2011/04/have-your-way/#comment-24321"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2011-04-07T15:09:52-04:00">Thursday, April 7, 2011 at 3:09 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Treat the greens like beet or other greens, if tender you can add to a salad and I once had a very tasty radish green quiche.  I&#39;ve seen radish greens in the freezer section at the Asian market.</p>
